BACKGROUND: The RECOURSE trial (Study of TAS-102 in Patients With Metastatic 
Colorectal Cancer Refractory to Standard Chemotherapies) demonstrated an overall 
survival (OS) benefit of trifluridine/tipiracil (FTD/TPI) vs placebo in 
refractory metastatic colorectal cancer (mCRC). Given the limited benefit of 
later line treatments, we developed the Colon Life nomogram to assess the 
