Chronic myeloid leukemia in solid organ transplant patients: a case series.

Amitai I(1)(2), Abulafia AS(3)(4), Raanani P(3)(4), Lipton JH(5).

Author information:
(1)Division of Hematology, Odette Cancer Centre, Sunnybrook Health Sciences 
Centre, 2075 Bayview Avenue TG 260, Toronto, ON, M4N 3M5, Canada. 
irinayoav@gmail.com.
(2)Sackler Faculty of Medicine, Tel Aviv University, Tel Aviv, Israel. 
irinayoav@gmail.com.
(3)Institute of Hematology, Davidoff Cancer Center, Rabin Medical Centre, Petah 
Tikva, Israel.
(4)Sackler Faculty of Medicine, Tel Aviv University, Tel Aviv, Israel.
(5)Allogeneic Blood and Marrow Transplant Service, Princess Margaret Cancer 
